title: GOOD SHELVES
description: Dive into the ultimate shelf-clearing challenge in Good Shelves - spot, match, and triumph one trio at a time! Good Shelves offers a captivating puzzle experience where your keen observation skills are your greatest allies. With just six slots to fill, you'll be on the hunt for sets of three identical objects among the shelves. But be wary, if your slots fill up without forming a trio, it's curtains for you! With over 100 exhilarating levels to conquer, immerse yourself in a world of meticulous matching. So, are you ready to declutter the shelves and prove your matching prowess in Good Shelves?
